Interacting - Use (A) to interact with creatures and objects alike. To get the full story, do this a lot.
Combat (ATTACK) - A cursor will fly up from the bottom of the screen. Press (A) when it is over your target.
Combat (ITEM) - Allows you to use items to heal or cause other effects. Would be really cool if you had any items.
Combat (CHECK) - Tells you some backstory on your current target and their current stats.
